flowchart TD
    Start([Start Linear Search]) --> Input[Input: Search Term<br/>e.g., title to find]
    Input --> Convert[Convert Search Term<br/>to Lowercase]
    Convert --> InitResults[Initialize Empty<br/>Results List]
    InitResults --> InitIndex[Set Index i = 0]
    InitIndex --> CheckLoop{i < List Size?}

    CheckLoop -->|No| CheckEmpty{Results List<br/>Empty?}
    CheckLoop -->|Yes| GetItem[Get Media Item<br/>at index i]

    GetItem --> GetTitle[Get Item Title<br/>Convert to Lowercase]
    GetTitle --> Compare{Title Contains<br/>Search Term?}

    Compare -->|No| Increment1[Increment i<br/>i = i + 1]
    Compare -->|Yes| AddResult[Add Item to<br/>Results List]

    AddResult --> Increment2[Increment i<br/>i = i + 1]
    Increment1 --> CheckLoop
    Increment2 --> CheckLoop

    CheckEmpty -->|Yes| DisplayNone[Display:<br/>No matches found]
    CheckEmpty -->|No| DisplayCount[Display:<br/>Found X results]

    DisplayNone --> End([End])
    DisplayCount --> DisplayLoop[Loop Through Results]
    DisplayLoop --> DisplayItem[Display Each Item:<br/>Title, Type, Status]
    DisplayItem --> End

    style Start fill:#90EE90
    style End fill:#FFB6C1
    style CheckLoop fill:#FFD700
    style Compare fill:#FFD700
    style CheckEmpty fill:#FFD700
    style GetItem fill:#87CEEB
    style AddResult fill:#90EE90
    style DisplayCount fill:#90EE90
    style DisplayNone fill:#FFA500
